# Dashboard Blade UI

## Page structure

- Each sidebar link = **separate route + Blade page** (`{role}/pages/{page}.blade.php`)
- Shared sidebar: `partials/dashboard-sidebar.blade.php` (links via named routes)
- Layout: `layouts/dashboard-page.blade.php`
- Config: `config/dashboards.php` → `pages`, `default_page`, assets

## Static UI phase (current)

- Empty states in Blade (`partials/dashboard-analytics-empty`, `dashboard-bi-empty`)
- JS `render*` / `ChartKit.mount` for analytics must **not** inject fake data
- Tables/lists start empty; counts show `0`
- Modals and form shells preserved for future wiring

## Role dashboards (7)

| Route prefix | Role |
|--------------|------|
| `/reception/*` | Reception |
| `/doctor/*` | Doctor |
| `/spec/*` | Technical spec |
| `/adjustments/*` | Adjustments |
| `/operations/*` | Operations desk |
| `/technical/*` | Inventory |
| `/admin/*` | System admin + BI |

## BI command boards (admin `/admin/bi`)

Five static cards: (1) patients/SLA, (2) inventory/WAC, (3) operations/WO, (4) entities/costs, (5) suppliers/WAC vs highest price.

Do not re-merge sections into single-page JS tab switching.
